snippet.title: S1E2: Amber Mac - Relentless Adaptation
snippet.description:
Best-selling author and tech expert Amber Mac shares a step-by-step process on how to keep your business alive and running during unprecedented times. While many leaders might feel helpless, there is an opportunity to adapt and become an organization that the country needs right now. Amber shares real-world examples of how businesses are pivoting to make a difference.

The model Amber shared can be found at https://f.hubspotusercontent20.net/hubfs/5104425/COVID-19-5STEPFRAMEWORK-AMMI-DRAFT1%20(1).pdf
